Myself, my dad & kids love coming here. The owners/employees are really courteous & friendly. The place is clean and set up well for covid precautions. Most Importantly, the food is fantastic 👌 they serve all diets, low fat, gluten free, different sauces, etc. The specialty pizza & garlic knots are my favorite..so was their white slice for a minute there, now it's their Buffalo slices & chicken/bacon/ranch 😋 Would recommend to order from here!

The location is a block away from the famed Pizza Wagon. I would say Mancinis is neck and neck with them.  They place itself is new and very beautiful. Nice decor and presentation of the food. There is plenty of room to sit and enjoy your food.  The food is really good. Had two slices and the came out of the oven super quick. It was the perfect cheese/sauce balance as well as the crisp factor was perfect.  The selections of pizza were vast. You have your regular slices as well as many specialty slices. Had some pasta with it and it was yummy. The menu is big and you cant go wrong with it.  They deliver and offer 10% off online delivery which makes it good for repeat customers!
